IEEE REGISTRATION AUTHORITY PUBLIC LISTINGS

macvendor can retrieve MA-L, MA-M, and MA-S public-listing data directly from:
https://standards.ieee.org/products-programs/regauth/

IEEE stated in a 2014 clarification preserved by Debian that it does not assert
copyright in the OUI Public Listing or attempt to restrict distribution of the
listing. IEEE strongly encourages direct retrieval and regular updates to
preserve data integrity. The evidence and residual-risk decision are recorded in
docs/rights/ieee-registration-authority.md.

IEEE data is not bundled in this source repository or GitHub release. Each
deployment records its own retrieval time, source URLs, SHA-256 hashes, and
validation report. macvendor is not affiliated with, sponsored by, or endorsed
by IEEE. IEEE and related marks belong to their respective owners.

The application source is MIT-licensed. That source-code license does not grant
additional rights in any fetched dataset.
